# Communication Style

## Non-Verbose Documentation and Interaction

- Keep documentation concise and to the point
- Avoid unnecessary explanations or verbose descriptions
- Focus on essential information only
- Use clear, direct language
- Prefer bullet points and tables over long paragraphs
- Skip redundant information and obvious statements

